s using simple code like this Earth. Editing Referencing Images Tables VisualEditor is the easier way of editing that works more like a word processor and hides the underlying source code. Links and other items are edited using toolbar and popup interfaces. Editing Referencing Images Tables Talk pages Navigating Wikipedia Manual of Style Conclusion View all as single page ns12 ns4 Shortcuts WPI HI HINTRO For more training information see also Full help contents page Training for students A singlepage guide to contributing A training adventure game Resources for new editors Please consider leaving us some feedback. Retrieved from httpsen.wikipedia.orgwindex.phptitleHelpIntroductionoldid1218518073 Category Wikipedia quick introductions Hidden category Wikipedia semiprotected project pages This page was last edited on 12 April 2024 at 0518 UTC. Text is available under the Creative Commons AttributionShareAlike License 
